headline: Updated NCCN Clinical Practice Guidelines in Oncology (NCCN Guidelines速) Recommend Use of FES PET Imaging for Lobular Breast Cancer
summary: ARLINGTON HEIGHTS, Ill., May 30, 2025--GE HealthCare announced that the NCCN Guidelines for Clinical Oncology now recommend FES PET for systemic staging in patients with metastatic ILC.
